title: The German Expressionists-A Generation in Revolt (Art Ebook)
description:
The German Expressionists: A Generation in Revolt
Frederick A. Praeger | 1957 | English | 410 pages | PDF | 71.5 MB

One of the first serious and detailed studies in any language on German Expressionism. Covers the historical and artistic background and explores the work of key Expressionist artists in Germany and Austria including Kokoschka, Meidner, Modersohn- Becker, Hofer etc
